// autofilters.filtersWindow.json — Auto Filters ribbon-launched configuration window
// (FiltersSettingsWindow.xaml.cs: toolbar chrome, undo/redo history, floating status chip,
// shared popup helpers) + its run handler (AutoFiltersEventHandler.cs: create/apply run log,
// link-safety warnings surfaced via ParamResolve.Warn, and the close-failure TaskDialog).
//
// The bulk of this window's UI (trades sidebar, rule editor, category picker, templates
// popup — same FiltersSettingsWindow class via the partial file GlobalSettingsWindow.Filters.cs)
// was already externalized to globalSettings.filters.json in a prior commit; this file covers
// only the pieces still living in FiltersSettingsWindow.xaml.cs itself.
//
// NOT localized (left as code):
//   - single-glyph icon strings ("×", "⚙", Segoe MDL2 codepoints via ConvertFromUtf32) —
//     decorative iconography, not language text.
//   - "AutoFilters: ..." LemoineLog context strings and Debug.WriteLine — debug-only, out of scope.
